    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "For sale is an exceptionally maintained E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This high-revving power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver a linear torque curve and an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-Differential Lock. This example has had critical preventative maintenance completed, including rod bearing replacement and comprehensive subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The suspension retains its factory-tuned geometry with refreshed bushings and Sachs dampers, providing the precise turn-in and chassis balance these cars are known for. Minor cosmetic patina consistent with mileage, but mechanically robust with a clean DME report and no VANOS rattle.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
