      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2017 Lexus RX 350 in Nebula Gray Pearl. This vehicle has been a reliable companion and is currently in great shape for its next owner. The exterior retains a beautiful luster, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical for a car of this age. Inside, the Parchment leather cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the seats remain plush, with only slight softening on the driver\u2019s outer bolster. Mechanically, the car is excellent. The V6 engine delivers smooth, consistent power, and the AWD system provides confident handling in all weather conditions. I have kept a detailed log of all maintenance, including a recent full synthetic oil change and a brake fluid flush. It also features a set of Michelin tires with plenty of tread remaining. Every feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the dual-zone climate control and navigation system, is in perfect working order. This is a solid, honest luxury SUV that balances comfort with legendary reliability.",
